---
title: "_call (Caller)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_call: (success, response) = target.call(data)
    q_call --> q_check: check success
    q_check --> q_return: success == true
    q_return --> [*]: return response
    q_check --> q_check_response: success == false
    q_check_response --> q_bubble_revert: response.length > 0
    q_bubble_revert --> [*]: revert(add(response, 32), returndataSize)
    q_check_response --> q_revert_generic: response.length == 0
    q_revert_generic --> [*]: revert LowLevelCallFailed()

    note right of q_call
        INV-001: low-level call to arbitrary target address
        INV-002: failed calls with return data bubble up the revert reason
        INV-003: failed calls without return data revert with LowLevelCallFailed
        INV-004: no value (ETH) is forwarded in the call
    end note
